item.title: CVE-2023-22320|2023-01-10T00:00:00 -- openam%20consortium -- openam%20web%20policy%20agent%20%28openam%20consortium%20edition%29
item.description: OpenAM Web Policy Agent (OpenAM Consortium Edition) provided by OpenAM Consortium parses URLs improperly, leading to a path traversal vulnerability(CWE-22). Furthermore, a crafted URL may be evaluated incorrectly.
